column5: Anyone have any fishing reports from this lake this year?--thanks
Here's a report from early Jun - see http://www.kipawa.net/viewtopic.php?t=1812

group of 4 fished for a week and we probly caught a total of 130 counting pike. largest walleye was 24 . 5 and biggest pike was 27. mullens are a great group of people, we will definately go back, they made the trip special for us.
